latestIgtvVideos.title: Independent India & women rights😇
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So whats today?
Independence day😍

Yes,its important to celebrate it wit great respect,values,and good prespectives..

So the most important is to make a girl,lady,women,female 
Independent

Around 73% of world thinks that females are only meant for marrige,children,and kitchen,

Like why ?
Don't they have the same emotions?
Same mind,same rights,?

We need to understand 
That witout a woman,
No man can exist this world..
Make women free,independent,
Get her to express each thing wit a true respect

Also my main motto is women education..
Bcz learning and growing,is the best a female can do..she has right to do her job,to earn,to get fulfilled all her dreams she had wished for..❤️

She thinks of holding pencil ✏️ 
Don’t let her holding rolling pin🙏🏼
She thinks of wearing a school dress..
Don’t her wear a wedding dress..
Her education should be her adornment..
Don’t her wear a mangalsutra ..
“Allow her to see her wings and she is born to rule in a kingdom”

And thats wen will be the true independence

Jai hind 👋
Jai bharat 🇮🇳
